# Cloudflare Pages SPA fallback.
#
# Serve the app shell for any path that is not a real static file. Real files
# (/assets, /img, /sitemap.xml, /robots.txt ...) are served before this rule.
#
# DO NOT rewrite explicit paths to `/index.html` (e.g. `/en  /index.html  200`).
# Cloudflare Pages normalizes `/index.html` to `/` with a 308, so such a rule
# turns `/en` into `/en -> 308 -> /`. That broke the canonical/hreflang URLs and
# fed the ERR_TOO_MANY_REDIRECTS loop inside the betterme.dev iframe.
#
# The splat below rewrites (serves index.html content, URL preserved, status 200)
# and does NOT trigger that normalization, so /en and /vi return 200.
/*    /index.html   200
